 HOW TO RUN
 * 1. Compile: javac ItemApiServer.java
 * 2. Run: java ItemApiServer
 * 3. Server URL: http://localhost:8000
 * 
 * API ENDPOINTS
 * 1) Add Item
 * POST /items
 * Body JSON:
 * {
 * "name": "Laptop",
 * "description": "Gaming Laptop"
 * }
 * 
 * 2) Get Item By ID
 * GET /items/{id}
 * Example: GET /items/1
 * 
 * INPUT VALIDATION
 * - name field is required and must not be empty
 * - description is optional
 * 
 * IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS
 * - In-memory storage using ArrayList<Item>
 * - No external libraries required
 * - Uses built-in com.sun.net.httpserver.HttpServer
 * =====================================================
 */
